B. Accomplishments/Planned Programs ($ in Millions)                                                                                FY 2025       FY 2026      FY 2027
- Maintain Operation Centers, ground networks, and ground terminal equipment to support Tranche 1 test and operations.
- Maintain development, security, and operations (DevSecOps) pipeline to support integrated Operations, Maintenance, and
