Title: CASR                                                                                                                                  6.000            23.282      10.427
Description: CASR provides a foundational capability across all mission areas to ensure commercial capabilities are fully
integrated into operations and available immediately during a crisis or conflict to combatant commands. It provides threat sharing,
wargame/exercise participation; contract readiness and incentives, etc., to CASR companies to fully integrate and assure
commercial capabilities are available across the spectrum of conflict at CCMD's timing/tempo to achieve operational objectives.
CASR ensures commercial solutions for joint requirements/capabilities are met during crisis or conflict. CASR predetermines



