COMSATCOM, SDA, and critical commercial contracts. Our ongoing engagement includes maintaining participation in wargaming
and exercises with approximately 15 commercial partners, alongside sustaining the CASR readiness and inspection program and
providing relevant incentives. We remain committed to rapidly responding to and implementing the necessary system resiliency
