and implement solutions for system resilience and situational awareness in contested environments. Provide pre-operations
support to meshONE-T mission partners. Activities may include, but are not limited to program office support, studies, technical
analysis, experimentation, risk reduction, prototyping, and activities that may leverage commercial, U.S. Government partnership,
