- Integrating into major theater exercise and operations to provide SpOC/CC, C-FLDCOMS, and CCMDs with the status of space
forces in near real-time.
- Building SAP/SAR standalone infrastructure to support fully articulated space effects in AFSIM (mission-level) and STORM
(campaign-level) models.
- Continuing SPAFORGEN assessment across 22 tactical units collecting, distilling, and analyzing after action reports and mission
