- Continuing to support MD 2, DEL 9 and other SpOC units with analyses and tool development provided on tactically relevant
timelines, enabling SpOC operators to execute their mission.
- Deliver SpOC/CC's automated SPAFORGEN Assessments Dashboard.
- Execute analysis of Delta 4's network infrastructure to identify critical points of failure that may force or impact Continuity of
Operation plans. As able, expand to include Delta 8 with remaining deltas to follow in subsequent years.
- Execute min-cut analysis of Delta 4's network infrastructure to identify critical points of failure that may force or impact Continuity
