FY 2025 to FY 2026 Increase/Decrease Statement:
FY 2026 decreased by $7.344 million compared to FY 2025 due to realignment of activities executed in this BPAC in FY
2025 to 644861, Operational Energy and associated increases with resuming Advanced Nuclear, Mission Resilience Digital
