OCX 3F baseline. The Enterprise Mission Planning Systems enable Over the Air Rekey capability and other navigation warfare
effects taskings. Additionally, initiate OCX 3F development for launching SV-13 Extended Bus (eBus) to the ground C2 systems
for Launch and Checkout and PNT capabilities.

Rapidly respond to implement system resiliency and situational awareness necessary to operate in the contested space domain.
