(T&E).

FY 2026 Plans:
Continue data collection and tuning of the monitoring stations equipment as needed. Continue Systems Engineering and technical
support and analysis for Government led testing, and operational demonstrations, exercises, and training. Assist with transition
events and provide technical support.
