of OCX 3F launch capabilities into the Operationally Accepted (OA) OCX baseline. Continue to support early GPS Enterprise
integration testing in support of MRC for GPS IIIF to include early development and testing specific to the evolved bus. Continue
to incorporate Enterprise Mission Planning Systems capability into OCX 3F baseline. Continue development of Cadre Training
and Technical Orders. The Enterprise Mission Planning Systems enable Over the Air Rekey capability and other navigation
warfare effects taskings. Rapidly respond to implement system resiliency and situational awareness necessary to operate in
the contested space domain. Activities may include, but are not limited to program office support, studies, technical analysis,



