FY 2027 Plans:
Complete software development to enable Global PNT C2 and continue software development for RMP checkout and Rapid
Warfighter Effects (RWE) initial operations. Continue integration activities that support the validation of requirements with use of
the OCX 3F GPS System Simulator. Deploy GPS IIIF Launch and Checkout System hardware. Prepare and continue coordination
