experimentation of counter ISR capabilities, along with Electronic Warfare (EW) and navigation warfare (NAVWAR) technology
integration and Positioning, Navigation and Timing (PNT) technology development and assessments, including experimentation
and prototyping in denied, degraded, intermittent, or limited (DDIL) operating environments.
