obstacles, such as landmines and other explosive hazards, using novel processing approaches. This project leverages existing
tactical airborne and geospatial intelligence data to provide locations to lower echelon maneuver formations to direct UAS threat
recognition and support breaching operations. It also provides content for inclusion within a modified combined obstacle overlay
for intelligence preparation and situational awareness.

